<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <p><em>This is an automated email message, please do not reply!</em></p>
    
    <h1>Dear <%= @pilot.name %></h1>
    <p>
      You have been assigned an instructor for your <%= @pilot.rating.name %> pilot training by the VATEUD PTD.<br/><br/>
      
      Your instructor is: <%= @pilot.instructor.name %>, VATSIM ID <%= @pilot.instructor.vatsimid %>.<br/>
      You can reach him by email: <%= @pilot.instructor.email %>
    </p>
    <p>
      After completing your training and your theoretical examination you will be assigned
      an examiner and an examination date for the online practical examination.
    </p>
    <p>
      You can always check the history and details of your personal record
      at the following address:
      <a href="http://ptd.vateud.net/pilots/<%=@pilot.slug %>">http://ptd.vateud.net/pilots/<%=@pilot.slug %></a>      
    </p>
    <p>Good luck and have a great day!</p>
    <p><em><strong>VATEUD Pilot Training Department Team</strong></em></p>
  </body>
</html>